skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: snack suggestion
des:
Snack suggestion can help you if you need a quick snack idea when you're hungry. The skill has a large library of snack ideas, both in the "healthy" and "yummy" categories, along with a few quirky jokes about our favorite foods.

To start, just say "Alexa, open snack suggestion". 
You can also ask for a specific type, either yummy or healthy like this: "Alexa, ask snack suggestion for a yummy snack".

Disclaimer: This skill may make you hungry. 

Built for: RAM Hacks Alexa Skill Initiative
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
